This document serves as a basis and reference for the logic and ideas behind the combat and class system within 404: Cards Not Found.

Names used for Cards/Attacks within the combat system will be in standard in every mentioned instance.

Names given to Positive Effects (Buffs) and Negative Effects (Debuffs) will be in *Italic* in every mentioned instance

Class and Enemy names will be ***Bold AND Italic*** and serve as a header for details below themselves.

Combat Mechanics will be written in **Bold** in all mentions.

